title: BRIEF-Sophie Baratte appointed Cellnovo CEO
text:
BRIEF-Sophie Baratte appointed Cellnovo CEO 
Oct 9 Cellnovo Group SA : 
* Cellnovo expands its organisation 
* Sophie Baratte appointed CEO 
* Cellnovo executive chairman to transition to non-executive chairman 
* Didier Lenormand joins Cellnovo as interim CFO in replacement of Bart Bergstein who has left company Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
